    "name": "Hemolysis model validation requirement — experimental confirmation mandatory",
    "description": "For a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5, the hemolysis prediction model must be validated by direct experimental-validation: physical bench-top or in-vitro hemolysis measurements must be compared against CFD-predicted hemolysis index values under matched operating conditions. Literature-based evidence alone is insufficient to satisfy this requirement.",
    "requiredVerificationMethod": "experimental-validation"
  },
