    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed the validation evidence package. The literature review was judged to provide comprehensive and complementary coverage of hemolysis mechanisms, and the systematic survey of 47 published studies was considered sufficient to support the CFD model's predictive capability. All 13 credibility factors were assessed; the team noted that achieved levels fall below required levels but concluded that the literature-based evidence base adequately supports the inference chain. The package is accepted pending future experimental confirmation.",
